text: José Fidel Sipi Bita (born 7 January 2001) is an Equatorial Guinean footballer who plays as a midfielder for Cano Sport Academy and the Equatorial Guinea national team. ==International career== Sipi made his international debut for Equatorial Guinea on 28 July 2019. ==References== Category:2001 births Category:Living people Category:Association football midfielders Category:Equatoguinean footballers Category:Equatorial Guinea international footballers Category:Cano Sport Academy players Category:Bubi people
